1
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:22,940
♪Only after bloom comes fruit♪

2
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:28,320
♪Who says glory must fade to the past♪

3
00:00:30,980 --> 00:00:36,070
♪Only through thunder
do you reach the clouds♪

4
00:00:37,270 --> 00:00:42,180
♪Who made you the crown of every peak♪

5
00:00:43,710 --> 00:00:46,990
♪I stand at the center of the stage♪

6
00:00:46,990 --> 00:00:50,060
♪My shadow is pinned against the wall♪

7
00:00:50,770 --> 00:00:55,720
♪Facing the light earns every medal♪

8
00:00:56,760 --> 00:00:59,940
♪Little birds,
save your needless pecking♪

9
00:00:59,940 --> 00:01:03,220
♪The open sky rises high♪

10
00:01:03,760 --> 00:01:08,890
♪When night falls,
the moon begins to shine♪

11
00:01:09,660 --> 00:01:12,920
♪I stand in the heart of these lands♪

12
00:01:12,920 --> 00:01:16,280
♪My shadow bears no crown or robe♪

13
00:01:16,690 --> 00:01:22,360
♪Then I know truth needs no disguise♪

14
00:01:22,770 --> 00:01:26,020
♪The green hills see me as I am♪

15
00:01:26,020 --> 00:01:29,350
♪Like dew, lightning,
and moon on the river♪

16
00:01:29,750 --> 00:01:33,790
♪Showing me exactly who I am♪

17
00:01:33,790 --> 00:01:35,040
=The Lead=

18
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:37,952
=Episode 44=

19
00:01:38,839 --> 00:01:39,759
Cut!

20
00:01:40,080 --> 00:01:40,719
- Passed.
- Good.

21
00:01:40,719 --> 00:01:42,160
Cut! The director called cut.

22
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:43,200
Scene 25 ready.

23
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:43,839
Move!

24
00:01:43,839 --> 00:01:45,320
Scene 105, shot 12, take 5.

25
00:01:46,279 --> 00:01:46,959
Move!

26
00:01:46,959 --> 00:01:47,640
- What are you looking at?
- Where are they?

27
00:01:47,679 --> 00:01:49,000
Props, move the props!

28
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:50,119
Hurry up! Everyone move!

29
00:01:50,800 --> 00:01:51,439
Zhu!

30
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,199
- You okay?
- Fine.

31
00:01:53,320 --> 00:01:54,839
Right, someone's been calling you.

32
00:01:55,440 --> 00:01:56,120
Thanks.

33
00:01:56,800 --> 00:01:57,519
Hurry!

34
00:01:57,519 --> 00:01:58,640
Don't stop! Hurry!

35
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:00,120
(Chu Jiahe: 12 missed calls)
Prepare for the next scene.

36
00:02:00,399 --> 00:02:01,359
Hey, Feng.

37
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,800
Come on, let's run through it.

38
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:03,744
(Chu Jiahe calling)

39
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,399
(Chu Jiahe: 13 missed calls)
He jumps down from here.

40
00:02:16,399 --> 00:02:17,640
The camera pans to your front.

41
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:19,119
You just land,

42
00:02:19,399 --> 00:02:21,079
then run off into the distance.

43
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:21,759
Got it?

44
00:02:24,079 --> 00:02:25,439
Be careful when you work.

45
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:27,439
Or you might be in danger, you know?

46
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:29,240
Xu.

47
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:29,880
Xiao.

48
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:30,560
How's your neck?

49
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:32,560
I haven't slept well these days.

50
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:33,759
I can barely move this part.

51
00:02:33,759 --> 00:02:34,600
Let me try.

52
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:36,759
I learned a new technique
recently, works great.

53
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:38,079
Gently, Xiao.

54
00:02:38,079 --> 00:02:40,120
I have to loosen these
two tendons back here.

55
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:42,319
Otherwise, you'll feel uncomfortable.

56
00:02:42,319 --> 00:02:43,239
Can't do anything.

57
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:46,000
- Is it okay?
- Feels good.

58
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:46,799
Is it okay?

59
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:48,920
Xiao, you're amazing!

60
00:02:48,920 --> 00:02:51,400
I feel so much lighter all of a sudden.

61
00:02:51,599 --> 00:02:52,599
Especially you,

62
00:02:52,959 --> 00:02:53,840
have to be careful.

63
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:56,599
Okay?

64
00:02:57,599 --> 00:02:58,120
Oh, my.

65
00:02:58,640 --> 00:02:59,840
I feel like...

66
00:03:05,599 --> 00:03:07,359
If you get hurt,
how can we shoot the rest?

67
00:03:07,599 --> 00:03:08,200
Right.

68
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:08,928
Right?

69
00:03:09,640 --> 00:03:10,760
Xiao is awesome.

70
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:13,879
A little harder, please?

71
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:18,920
Alright, just get more rest.

72
00:03:19,480 --> 00:03:21,280
Xiao, give me a massage too.

73
00:03:21,719 --> 00:03:22,519
I'm not good at it.

74
00:04:33,696 --> 00:04:35,776
(Gaoming Eyewear)

75
00:05:42,439 --> 00:05:44,759
Xiao, you're here.

76
00:05:47,199 --> 00:05:48,199
Why are you so soaked?

77
00:05:48,199 --> 00:05:49,560
Go change your clothes upstairs.

78
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:50,240
Jiahe.

79
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:54,480
I-I came today

80
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,279
to tell you something.

81
00:06:03,639 --> 00:06:04,720
I want a breakup.

82
00:06:12,399 --> 00:06:13,120
I'm sorry.

83
00:06:18,279 --> 00:06:19,399
What are you sorry for?

84
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,279
You don't love me?

85
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:26,720
You helped me,

86
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:28,879
and I owe you this.

87
00:06:34,399 --> 00:06:35,399
Then who do you love?

88
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:37,839
Yi Qin'e?

89
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:47,279
Why didn't you tell Yi Qin'e everything

90
00:06:48,519 --> 00:06:50,120
at the provincial troupe?

91
00:06:52,879 --> 00:06:54,240
You left without saying a word.

92
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:57,319
Because you lost your voice,

93
00:06:57,856 --> 00:06:59,200
and didn't want to drag her down,

94
00:06:59,959 --> 00:07:00,576
right?

95
00:07:06,879 --> 00:07:10,079
Do you think you're being noble
and making a big sacrifice?

96
00:07:13,639 --> 00:07:16,120
You should've told her everything

97
00:07:16,399 --> 00:07:17,439
and let her choose.

98
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:20,279
She has the right to choose.

99
00:07:31,519 --> 00:07:32,519
Admit it.

100
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:35,240
You're just afraid of being rejected,

101
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:39,000
so you didn't love her enough.

102
00:07:42,160 --> 00:07:43,560
If that's how you treated her,

103
00:07:44,319 --> 00:07:45,560
who could you ever truly love?

104
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,480
I am truly stupid

105
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,480
that I only figure it out now.

106
00:07:58,879 --> 00:08:00,560
Last time you celebrated my birthday,

107
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:05,344
when I blew out the lighter
in your hand, I made a wish.

108
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:12,920
I wished you could celebrate
my birthday with me every year.

109
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,240
In a way, it came true.

110
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:21,879
You're here,

111
00:08:24,319 --> 00:08:25,759
but to break up with me.

112
00:08:35,279 --> 00:08:36,720
Don't feel guilty.

113
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:39,279
Honestly, I don't love you that much.

114
00:08:40,800 --> 00:08:42,600
Life is pretty hard

115
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:45,560
in Shenzhen.

116
00:08:47,439 --> 00:08:48,720
Or maybe because of loneliness.

117
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:58,120
You can go.

118
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,279
We owe each other nothing.

119
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:14,639
(Many years later,)

120
00:11:15,039 --> 00:11:17,639
(when Yi Qin'e sees Chu Jiahe again,)

121
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:20,840
(she's already made a name
for herself in Shenzhen,)

122
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:24,039
(becoming a businesswoman
capable of building skyscrapers.)

123
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:28,440
(She's truly become
the protagonist of her own life.)

124
00:11:29,759 --> 00:11:33,120
(Feng Xiaoxiao later became
a renowned martial arts director.)

125
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:34,519
(He has his own family now.)

126
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:37,519
(He's a good husband and father.)

127
00:11:38,879 --> 00:11:40,840
(But as for the story between them,)

128
00:11:40,919 --> 00:11:43,104
(once the candles were blown out,)

129
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:45,399
(it also ended.)

130
00:11:45,679 --> 00:11:49,240
(Those stories of infatuated lovers
in opera excerpts)

131
00:11:49,279 --> 00:11:50,679
(are always like this.)

132
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:53,840
(Reunion on stage,
and parting off stage.)

133
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,720
(When the spotlights dim,)

134
00:11:56,399 --> 00:11:59,559
(each goes on their own path.)

135
00:12:15,776 --> 00:12:16,360
Come, harder!

136
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:17,759
A bit lower on the left.

137
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:19,000
Come on, get ready.

138
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:21,320
- Too high.
- Okay.

139
00:12:21,679 --> 00:12:23,399
- Watch the floor!
- Got it.

140
00:12:23,399 --> 00:12:24,159
Okay now.

141
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:25,480
Qin'e.

142
00:12:26,399 --> 00:12:27,240
Troupe Leader, Uncle.

143
00:12:28,039 --> 00:12:29,240
Troupe Leader, perfect timing.

144
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:30,799
I need to talk to you.

145
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:32,200
We got another booking.

146
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:33,840
Same village in Ningzhou as last time.

147
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:36,360
They requested the full opera You Xi Hu.

148
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:40,679
When's your kid's surgery?

149
00:12:40,679 --> 00:12:41,519
How's your schedule?

150
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:42,840
I can manage it.

151
00:12:43,159 --> 00:12:44,480
We'll schedule it after the show.

152
00:12:45,159 --> 00:12:46,720
We must go! Absolutely!

153
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:48,679
That village is your lucky place.

154
00:12:49,279 --> 00:12:52,159
After last show there, the doctor
said the kid could have surgery.

155
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:54,919
Then after this show,
the surgery will surely succeed.

156
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:55,840
Right.

157
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:57,960
We'll send the troupe's best performers.

158
00:12:58,360 --> 00:13:00,240
Alright, I'll head home first.

159
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:00,759
- Okay.
- Okay.

160
00:13:00,759 --> 00:13:01,600
- Leaving now.
- Okay.

161
00:13:08,159 --> 00:13:10,120
Master Chen, I'm leaving.

162
00:13:12,159 --> 00:13:12,960
I didn't let him in.

163
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:22,720
Hey, beauty.

164
00:13:24,279 --> 00:13:25,480
May I take you to dinner?

165
00:13:26,759 --> 00:13:27,840
Why dressed like that?

166
00:13:28,279 --> 00:13:29,559
It's my wedding outfit.

167
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:31,279
What? Forgot it?

168
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:34,080
I found it accidentally today.

169
00:13:34,080 --> 00:13:35,639
I tried it on, and it still fits.

170
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:38,399
You've lost weight.

171
00:13:39,159 --> 00:13:40,120
Haven't shaved again.

172
00:13:42,559 --> 00:13:43,080
Let's go.

173
00:13:43,879 --> 00:13:44,559
Where to?

174
00:13:44,919 --> 00:13:45,639
Somewhere nice.

175
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:47,200
Piles of chores at home.

176
00:13:47,720 --> 00:13:49,840
It won't take long, come on.

177
00:14:05,280 --> 00:14:08,384
♪How could I fall for you?♪

178
00:14:09,216 --> 00:14:12,224
♪I'm asking myself♪

179
00:14:12,768 --> 00:14:16,288
♪I can give up anything♪

180
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:18,960
♪Yet today I can't bear to leave♪

181
00:14:18,960 --> 00:14:20,320
In here, what are you looking at?

182
00:14:20,320 --> 00:14:21,279
Look at the stage.

183
00:14:21,279 --> 00:14:22,440
♪You're not beautiful♪

184
00:14:22,440 --> 00:14:23,080
How's that?

185
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:27,639
When did you get into the music scene?

186
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:31,200
I'm just a sidekick now.

187
00:14:32,159 --> 00:14:33,240
He's the protagonist.

188
00:14:33,240 --> 00:14:34,039
♪My Cinderella♪

189
00:14:34,039 --> 00:14:34,624
Look.

190
00:14:36,519 --> 00:14:37,080
At what?

191
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:40,080
You still don't recognize him?

192
00:14:42,240 --> 00:14:42,919
Easy.

193
00:14:43,648 --> 00:14:47,008
♪I always hurt your feelings♪

194
00:14:47,616 --> 00:14:49,360
♪I'm always so cruel♪

195
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:50,399
Is that Cungen?

196
00:14:50,799 --> 00:14:51,720
Who else?

197
00:14:52,360 --> 00:14:54,279
He won't let us call him that.

198
00:14:54,879 --> 00:14:55,720
Then what?

199
00:14:56,159 --> 00:14:56,840
Easy.

200
00:14:57,480 --> 00:14:58,879
What does it mean?

201
00:14:59,720 --> 00:15:00,399
Simple.

202
00:15:01,159 --> 00:15:02,120
Simple?

203
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:03,960
Simple.

204
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:06,144
♪And you're utterly adorable♪

205
00:15:07,936 --> 00:15:09,952
♪Cinderella♪

206
00:15:10,784 --> 00:15:13,824
♪My Cinderella♪

207
00:15:30,200 --> 00:15:32,080
He's just like you,

208
00:15:32,679 --> 00:15:34,240
born with a great voice,

209
00:15:34,480 --> 00:15:36,200
always singing.

210
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:39,080
Now I'm his sidekick.

211
00:15:39,360 --> 00:15:40,320
He's my boss now.

212
00:15:41,120 --> 00:15:42,600
♪I'd rather stay drunk forever♪

213
00:15:42,600 --> 00:15:43,720
He is better than me.

214
00:15:44,159 --> 00:15:44,960
When I was little,

215
00:15:44,960 --> 00:15:48,360
Aunt Mi Lan and Aunt Hua
both said I had a poor singing voice.

216
00:15:48,736 --> 00:15:50,112
And I don't like singing either.

217
00:15:50,879 --> 00:15:52,720
The troupe called me mute.

218
00:15:53,399 --> 00:15:54,639
All I could do was herd sheep.

219
00:15:56,896 --> 00:15:58,039
♪I wait♪

220
00:15:58,039 --> 00:15:59,399
Let's go back to Jiuyangou.

221
00:16:00,128 --> 00:16:01,360
♪Perhaps for your arrival♪

222
00:16:01,360 --> 00:16:02,639
Go check on the lambs.

223
00:16:03,159 --> 00:16:04,799
My dad doesn't raise sheep anymore.

224
00:16:05,759 --> 00:16:07,039
No one buys them now.

225
00:16:08,200 --> 00:16:09,519
Raising sheep isn't profitable.

226
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:12,559
Pens are still there.

227
00:16:14,480 --> 00:16:15,480
When do you set out?

228
00:16:16,080 --> 00:16:16,879
Day after tomorrow.

229
00:16:20,279 --> 00:16:22,480
Alright, when you're back,

230
00:16:23,440 --> 00:16:24,639
and our kid has surgery,

231
00:16:25,639 --> 00:16:26,799
our whole family

232
00:16:26,799 --> 00:16:27,879
will visit Jiuyangou.

233
00:16:27,879 --> 00:16:30,320
♪I'm asking myself♪

234
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:31,279
We'll see.

235
00:16:31,296 --> 00:16:34,784
♪I can give up anything♪

236
00:16:34,880 --> 00:16:38,208
♪Yet today I can't bear to leave♪

237
00:16:38,976 --> 00:16:41,984
♪You're not beautiful♪

238
00:16:42,496 --> 00:16:46,112
♪But you're utterly adorable♪

239
00:16:47,648 --> 00:16:49,912
♪Cinderella♪

240
00:16:50,688 --> 00:16:53,664
♪My Cinderella♪

241
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:08,120
The Red Berries Bloom.

242
00:17:09,840 --> 00:17:12,240
This whole area
used to be military factories.

243
00:17:12,736 --> 00:17:15,264
Many engineers who had studied
in the Soviet Union live here.

244
00:17:17,840 --> 00:17:19,320
How romantic!

245
00:17:26,799 --> 00:17:28,440
Miss Yi,

246
00:17:28,440 --> 00:17:31,399
may I dance with you?

247
00:17:34,039 --> 00:17:35,679
Stop acting crazy.

248
00:17:36,799 --> 00:17:38,559
How is this acting crazy?

249
00:17:38,559 --> 00:17:40,519
I'm being romantic.

250
00:17:43,399 --> 00:17:46,080
♪By the field and the river♪

251
00:17:46,080 --> 00:17:48,679
♪Where the red berries bloom♪

252
00:17:49,000 --> 00:17:51,440
♪There's a young maiden♪

253
00:17:51,639 --> 00:17:54,480
♪Who has captured my heart♪

254
00:17:59,240 --> 00:18:04,000
♪Her song of Mu Guiying
lingers in my heart♪

255
00:19:18,359 --> 00:19:20,599
Son, Dad's here!

256
00:19:20,599 --> 00:19:22,839
Look what delicious food I brought you.

257
00:19:23,519 --> 00:19:24,319
Where's your mom?

258
00:19:27,880 --> 00:19:28,759
You're here.

259
00:19:29,839 --> 00:19:31,240
You wipe his face.

260
00:19:31,240 --> 00:19:31,840
Okay.

261
00:19:32,319 --> 00:19:33,279
Here, let me do it.

262
00:19:33,559 --> 00:19:34,336
When do you leave?

263
00:19:34,559 --> 00:19:35,599
Now.

264
00:19:36,279 --> 00:19:37,519
You'll handle it tonight.

265
00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:39,519
No big deal.

266
00:19:41,039 --> 00:19:42,480
I'll be back early tomorrow.

267
00:19:43,119 --> 00:19:44,000
Come back soon.

268
00:19:44,440 --> 00:19:46,160
The kid and I are waiting for you.

269
00:19:46,680 --> 00:19:47,680
What do you want to eat?

270
00:19:48,119 --> 00:19:49,119
What would you like?

271
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:52,640
How about
vinegar-fried shredded potatoes?

272
00:19:54,440 --> 00:19:55,640
Don't make him laugh too hard.

273
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:56,759
His heart can't handle it.

274
00:19:57,519 --> 00:19:58,839
I'm leaving.

275
00:20:01,519 --> 00:20:02,920
Behave, okay?

276
00:20:03,936 --> 00:20:04,480
Here.

277
00:20:07,039 --> 00:20:09,000
I brought you breakfast for the road.

278
00:20:16,440 --> 00:20:17,640
Wake up, time to get up.

279
00:20:17,640 --> 00:20:18,519
Time to draw blood.

280
00:20:18,759 --> 00:20:19,880
Don't make him laugh hard.

281
00:20:19,880 --> 00:20:20,559
Take care.

282
